net.realmproject.dcm.features.command

Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.realmproject.dcm.features.command.Command
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Identity, Properties<java.lang.Object>, Recordable

    public class Command
extends java.lang.Object
implements Properties<java.lang.Object>, Recordable, Identity
    Class representing a command issued to a device. A command is similar to a method invocation (or a smalltalk message). It contains an action name analogous to method name (or selector), and arguments/properties analogous to named arguments (or keywords). Devices implementing the CommandDevice interface can apply the CommandMethod and Arg annotations to methods to enable automatic dispatch of commands to methods
    Author:
    NAS
